dc_description_s: For questions about this data please contact RegulatoryServicesOpenData@minneapolismn.gov Current on-sale liquor licenses active in the city. Field Descriptions Attribute descriptions in respective order: FID - feature ID Shape - geometry of feature PERMITID - ID number of permit TYPE - license type code PERMIT - permit number DECISION - status of license LIQUOR_TYP - distinguishes on-sale from off-sale STATUS - open or closed, all in dataset are open ISSUEDATE - issue date of license EXPIRE_YEA - expiration year of license EXPIRE_DAT - not used ESTABLISHM - number of the establishment holding license ESTABLISH_1 - name of establishment holding license ESTABLISH_2 - address of establishment holding license ESTABLISH_3 -address suite number where applicable ESTABLISH_4 - street direction where applicable TYPE_DESCR - additional license description LastUpdate - when data was last updated WGS_X - X coordinate (WGS84 web mercator auxilliary sphere) WGS_Y - Y coordinate (WGS84 web mercator auxilliary sphere) APN - parcel ID number
